contact www.OpenSubtitles.org today

15:50.240 --> 15:54.519
- Hey. Can I help you?
- Yeah. Why does everybody think I'm gay?

15:55.520 --> 15:57.671
God, I hate yard sales.

16:01.560 --> 16:03.552
Thank you.
Mm-hmm.

16:04.880 --> 16:07.081
Sorry for snooping around
and finding your old-man doll.

16:07.160 --> 16:09.959
In Colombia, if you snoop
around the wrong box,

16:10.040 --> 16:12.475
you might end up
inside that box.

16:12.560 --> 16:15.200
I shouldn't have done it.
Now I feel bad for Manny.

16:16.320 --> 16:19.040
- What do you mean?
- Well, I don't know.

16:19.120 --> 16:20.840
He's always talking about
how brave you are,

16:20.920 --> 16:22.559
how you're not afraid
of anything.

16:22.680 --> 16:25.798
Now he just seems a little sad.
How sad?

16:25.920 --> 16:27.832
Don't worry.
It's a good thing.

16:27.920 --> 16:29.718
He needs a little dose
of reality.

16:29.840 --> 16:33.117
You walk around school telling everyone
how great your mommy is all the time,

16:33.200 --> 16:35.556
you find yourself on the
business end of a wedgie.

16:38.040 --> 16:40.509
I know how to push buttons
to get what I want,

16:40.600 --> 16:43.399
and what I want
is to see a puppet show.

16:45.200 --> 16:46.111
J'accuse!

16:46.200 --> 16:48.192
I'm sorry.
One more time?

16:48.280 --> 16:52.160
It's just a dramatic way of accusing you
of stashing my fat pants in a bush!

16:52.320 --> 16:54.118
Saboteur!
That's a second way.

16:54.240 --> 16:55.879
How... could... you?

16:55.960 --> 16:57.110
And a third.

16:57.240 --> 17:00.199
Why, Mitchell? Why?
Cam-Oh, come on.

17:00.280 --> 17:01.509
All right, the-

17:01.600 --> 17:03.637
This is a little hard
to say, but...

17:03.720 --> 17:06.997
every time you get rid of these pants,
you have to buy them all over again,

17:07.079 --> 17:09.549
and you get depressed,
all right?

17:09.640 --> 17:12.314
This is just a way
to have a safety net.

17:12.400 --> 17:13.880
I can't have a safety net,
Mitchell.

17:13.960 --> 17:16.201
Otherwise, I won't be successful
and keep the weight off.

17:16.280 --> 17:17.794
Have you ever thought of that?

17:19.040 --> 17:20.952
No. No, I didn't.

17:21.040 --> 17:24.511
You know, you're not the only one who
remembers all the times I failed.

17:26.079 --> 17:27.560
You're right.

17:27.640 --> 17:29.950
I-I should support you more.
I'm-I'm sorry.

17:30.080 --> 17:32.680
Well, I'm happy to hear you say that.
Well, I'm happy you're happy.

17:32.720 --> 17:33.960
Well, I hope
you both are happy.

17:34.040 --> 17:35.918
Michael's not gay.
Now he hates me.

17:36.000 --> 17:37.514
Thanks a lot.

17:37.600 --> 17:41.196
You see? This is exactly why I
didn't want to get involved.

17:42.800 --> 17:45.076
Now I feel terrible.

17:45.160 --> 17:47.470
These feelings would go good
with pie.

17:49.280 --> 17:51.749
There he is!

17:54.360 --> 17:56.955
Sweetheart, do you love it?

17:57.040 --> 17:58.440
No, Claire, I do not love it.

17:58.520 --> 18:01.115
Oh, that's too bad, 'cause
you look so cool on that.

18:01.200 --> 18:03.760
Do I, Claire? Do I really?

18:03.880 --> 18:06.520
What happened? It's a long story.
Check your in-box.

18:06.640 --> 18:09.235
But suffice it to say, I'm not
buying that motorcycle. Uh-huh.

18:09.320 --> 18:13.030
I know what I am, Claire. I'm not a rider.
I'm a strider.

18:13.120 --> 18:15.555
I hope that's
sexy enough for you.

18:15.680 --> 18:18.559
Well, I can see stuff. Yeah, I know.
I can feel air on it.

18:18.680 --> 18:20.521
Mmm. It's not like I have
another pair of pants.

18:20.560 --> 18:22.870
Well, uh, today is
your lucky day.

18:22.960 --> 18:24.440
It's for a good cause.

18:24.520 --> 18:26.034
You might need a belt.

18:26.120 --> 18:28.157
Oh, I doubt it.
I bet we wear the same size.

18:28.240 --> 18:30.914
- Don't do that.
- Copy.

18:32.040 --> 18:34.635
Well, we ruined Alex's life,
by the way.

18:34.720 --> 18:37.110
I don't know.
She looks okay.

18:37.240 --> 18:39.800
- Oh, looks like they made up.
- Hmm.

18:39.880 --> 18:42.440
Wish she would just listen to me. I
could help her avoid so much pain.

18:42.520 --> 18:44.273
Give it a rest.
She's 14, all right?

18:44.400 --> 18:47.393
No matter who that boy is, he's not gonna last.
Mmm. You're right.

18:47.520 --> 18:48.954
Well, at least with a gay kid,

18:49.040 --> 18:50.713
you know she's gonna get
a great flower arrangement.

18:50.800 --> 18:52.473
Should've seen the one
I made Annabelle.

18:52.560 --> 18:54.870
Arranged it myself.
It was gorgeous.

18:54.960 --> 18:58.590
Till she pulled it apart
and spelled "homo" on my porch.

18:58.680 --> 19:00.558
This doesn't make me
feel any better.

19:00.640 --> 19:02.313
Gather around, everybody.

19:02.400 --> 19:04.392
I want you to meet somebody.

19:04.480 --> 19:07.314
Oh, but that might.
Uncle Grumpy!

19:08.680 --> 19:11.070
Luke's wise words got to me.

19:11.160 --> 19:14.153
I needed my son
to respect me again.

19:14.240 --> 19:17.950
More than that,
I needed to respect myself.

19:18.040 --> 19:19.952
Holy maracas!

19:20.040 --> 19:22.953
I think I sat on the right lap!

19:23.040 --> 19:26.477
Uncle Grumpy, we're in public.

19:26.600 --> 19:29.513
Ay, look at
all those white faces!

19:29.600 --> 19:32.718
I see we made it over the wall!

19:32.800 --> 19:34.837
Uncle Grumpy,
are you in a bad mood?

19:34.920 --> 19:39.153
Damn right, I am!
I just came from the movies.

19:39.280 --> 19:43.718
A whole day's pay
to see Basic instinct.

19:43.800 --> 19:46.360
Oh. And what did you think?

19:46.440 --> 19:48.397
Basically, it stinks.

19:49.760 --> 19:51.513
You're so grumpy.

19:51.600 --> 19:53.319
Damn right, I am!

19:53.400 --> 19:56.279
I just met
the girl of my dreams.

19:56.360 --> 19:57.919
Ay, that's such great news.

19:58.000 --> 20:01.357
No!
She gave me the termites.

20:02.600 --> 20:04.000
Gloria, I'm just gonna-

20:04.080 --> 20:06.311
Oh, geez. I don't even wanna know
what this is. I'm outta here.

20:06.440 --> 20:07.715
You're leaving?
Damn right.

20:07.800 --> 20:09.712
The only difference between
this and a home invasion...

20:09.800 --> 20:12.713
is I get to shoot people
at a home invasion.

20:12.800 --> 20:15.952
Oh, my God.
She married her puppet.

20:18.480 --> 20:20.039
Encore!
Encore!

20:20.120 --> 20:21.998
Uncle Grumpy!

20:25.160 --> 20:28.676
Can anyone hear me?

20:28.760 --> 20:30.911
Please help me!

20:31.040 --> 20:32.759
I don't wanna die!

20:32.840 --> 20:36.550
If I had to make a playlist for
being trapped under a motorcycle,

20:36.640 --> 20:38.711
it'd be, um,

20:38.840 --> 20:41.560
"Stuck in the Middle,"
"Hit the Road, Jack"-

20:41.640 --> 20:44.712
Um, anything by Heavy D.

20:44.800 --> 20:46.951
Ooh. Pointer Sisters,
"Neutron Dance."

20:47.040 --> 20:52.559
Turns out today wasn't the first
day of the rest of my life.

20:52.640 --> 20:54.518
Oh, my goodness.

20:54.600 --> 20:57.434
There are some DVDs in a shoe
box in, uh, my closet...

20:57.520 --> 20:59.830
that I was holding for a buddy.

20:59.920 --> 21:02.515
Um, you can go ahead and just
throw the whole box away.

21:13.320 --> 21:16.074
I'm so hungry.

21:16.160 --> 21:19.073
I don't know how long
I'm gonna be out here.

21:19.160 --> 21:21.436
I gotta ration my food.

21:28.880 --> 21:31.998
I said "No tomatoes"!

